- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper is primarily focused on the design and implementation of control systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the use of embedded systems in control engineering, which is a common application area in robotics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions the use of complex control algorithms, which may involve machine learning techniques. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the use of free and open source software packages and the development of drivers for interfacing with communication protocols, which are common topics in software engineering.
